    "先看这里：总览和趋势都在首页。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先看这里：总览和趋势都在首页。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先看這裡：總覽和趨勢都在首頁。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Start here: your overview and trends live on the dashboard."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "先看总资产、净资产和趋势概览，适合每天快速掌握资产变化。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先看总资产、净资产和趋势概览，适合每天快速掌握资产变化。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先看總資產、淨資產和趨勢概覽，適合每天快速掌握資產變化。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Start with your total assets, net worth, and trend overview for a quick daily check-in."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "完成后可从底部标签随时切换页面。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完成后可从底部标签随时切换页面。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完成後可從底部標籤隨時切換頁面。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "After the tutorial, you can switch pages anytime from the bottom tabs."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "当前页": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
